.TH MNEMOSYNE-WIKI-RESOLVE 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne wiki-resolve \- Update one conflict's resolution metadata without deleting evidence.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne wiki-resolve\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Update one conflict's resolution metadata without deleting evidence.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-wiki\-root\fR
LLM Wiki root (default: ~/mnemosyne/wiki)
.TP
\fB\-\-db\-path\fR
KnowledgeGraph DB path
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR
.TP
\fB\-\-lock\-timeout\fR
Seconds to wait for the wiki write lock on write commands
.TP
\fBconflict_id\fR
Stable conflict ID from `mnemosyne wiki contradictions`
.TP
\fB\-\-resolution\fR
.TP
\fB\-\-note\fR
Optional review note
.TP
\fB\-\-reviewer\fR
Optional reviewer label
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Preview the metadata update without writing
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
